Here are the key **features** you can include in a full-stack **Task Management & Collaboration** project.

### Authentication

* User registration
* Secure login/logout
* JWT authentication
* Password hashing
* Forgot password & reset password
* Email verification (optional)
* Google/GitHub OAuth login

### User Management

* User profile
* Edit profile
* Upload profile picture
* Change password
* Role-based access (Admin/User)

### Project Management

* Create, edit, and delete projects
* Archive projects
* Add project description
* Invite team members
* Assign project owner

### Task Management

* Create, edit, and delete tasks
* Assign tasks to users
* Set due dates
* Task priorities (Low, Medium, High)
* Task status (To Do, In Progress, Review, Completed)
* Drag-and-drop Kanban board
* Task labels/tags
* Subtasks
* Recurring tasks

### Collaboration

* Task comments
* File attachments
* @Mentions in comments
* Team workspace
* Activity timeline
* Shared projects

### Notifications

* In-app notifications
* Email notifications
* Due date reminders
* Task assignment alerts
* Project updates

### Search & Filters

* Search projects
* Search tasks
* Filter by status
* Filter by priority
* Filter by assignee
* Sort by due date or creation date

### Dashboard

* Overview of active projects
* Pending tasks
* Completed tasks
* Upcoming deadlines
* Team productivity summary
* Charts and analytics

### Admin Features

* Manage users
* View all projects
* Manage roles and permissions
* View activity logs
* Dashboard analytics
* Deactivate or delete users

### Security

* Protected routes
* Input validation
* Rate limiting
* CSRF/XSS protection
* Secure password storage
* Session expiration

### Responsive UI

* Mobile-friendly design
* Dark mode
* Light mode
* Accessibility support

### Optional Advanced Features

* Real-time updates with WebSockets
* Live chat between team members
* Calendar view
* Gantt chart
* Time tracking
* Export reports (PDF/CSV)
* AI-powered task suggestions
* Multi-language support
* Offline support (PWA)
* Integration with Slack, Google Calendar, or GitHub

These features provide a complete full-stack project that demonstrates authentication, CRUD operations, authorization, real-time communication, responsive design, and modern application architecture.

